      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some noticeable scuffs, a few small dings, and the paint is starting to fade on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows typical wear and tear, and while the engine runs well, it may require some minor maintenance soon to keep it in peak shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a more affordable price point.",
