    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. Delivering a linear power band via individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, this engine remains in peak mechanical harmony. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise engagement, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone a rigorous inspection confirming a crack-free rear subframe and pristine rod bearings. The suspension geometry remains true, retaining its original damping characteristics and bushings for a visceral, analog driving experience. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a flawless interior, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
